text: In the US, when this first started, the CDC was asking ppl to stop buying masks because the supply was so low for medical professionals. During non-pandemic times, people wear masks (ie in SEA) to make sure they don't get others sick but considering asymptomatic ppl are major path of spread as well as it's aerosol life, it makes sense for all of us to wear masks. With that being said, I just posted in another channel that we can create a DIY how to using netelas and think this campaign is a great idea. Just needs to be done right so ppl don't think they're safe just because of a face mask.

attachments.fallback: [April 1st, 2020 11:26 AM] eseteg0: Good afternoon, my name is Dr.Esete Getachew. The 29th case the MOH announced today she is my close friend. She was quarantined on Monday at the Arabasa site. She was told yesterday that result was negative after less than 24 hours of taking sample and running the test and was sent home. Now today they called her and told her it was the wrong result. After they took her to Kotebe, five hours later the second test becomes positive. This kind of mistakes will cost us dearly. What if they didn't get the results early , what if she went to see her mother who is an Astmatic, diabetic person. How many people have e being sent back to the public with this kind of results. More measures should be taken.
